I have added the following code to the HelpUIPlugin:

	public void stop(BundleContext context) throws Exception {
		plugin = null;
		//Make sure we cancel indexer if it is currently running
		Platform.getJobManager().cancel(IndexerJob.FAMILY);
		super.stop(context);
	}

This should ensure that indexer is stopped if currently running or scheduled 
to run.
